accessibility.text: I guess it's worth giving a try
By the time the next week rolls around, you notice that your classmates are less eager to talk to you once they realize you're very different from the typical American they had in mind… Oh well…
During lunch, you see a flyer for a Cultural Club meeting, set for tomorrow afternoon.
Do you go to the meeting?
No.. I'd be so different from those who are actually Chinese
